.
</emphasis>
In Reitter’s collection at 
<collectionCode LSID="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34991" box="[581,673,330,356]" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34991" name="Hungarian Natural History Museum (Termeszettudomanyi Muzeum)" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">HNHM</collectionCode>
is a male (mounted on card with the aedeagus dissected, right middle leg and all claws except those of left fore legs missing) bearing the labels: “Turkestan, Reitter.Leder” printed, “ 
<taxonomicName box="[270,369,405,430]" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Lixus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="confinis" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[270,369,405,430]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">confinis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[377,445,405,431]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
” handwritten, “ 
<typeStatus box="[643,778,405,431]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Holotypus</typeStatus>
, 
<number box="[792,857,405,431]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="1904.0">1904</number>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Petri" authorityName="Petri" box="[871,1258,405,431]" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Lixus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="confinis" subGenus="Phillixus">
<emphasis box="[871,938,405,430]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Lixus</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[957,1068,405,430]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Phillixus</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[1088,1187,405,430]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">confinis</emphasis>
Petri
</taxonomicName>
” red brimmed museum label, “Coll. Reitter” printed, fitting the description of 
<typeStatus box="[956,1009,442,468]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">type</typeStatus>
locality as “Turkestan”. It is here designated as 
<typeStatus box="[319,428,480,506]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">lectotype</typeStatus>
with “ 
<typeStatus box="[507,645,480,506]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Lectotypus</typeStatus>
, 
<number box="[657,679,479,505]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="3.0">3</number>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Petri, Gultekin" authorityName="Petri, Gultekin" box="[695,1046,480,506]" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Lixus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="confinis">
<emphasis box="[695,861,480,505]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Lixus confinis</emphasis>
Petri, Gültekin
</taxonomicName>
des. 
<number box="[1109,1173,480,506]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="2008.0">2008</number>
”, “ 
<taxonomicName authority="Cap., Gultekin" authorityName="Cap., Gultekin" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Lixus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kraatzi">
<emphasis box="[1210,1366,480,505]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Lixus kraatzi</emphasis>
Cap., Gültekin
</taxonomicName>
